  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e01\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462372864/hD02A9974/cash-flow-little-tete-tete-with-our-boss\" id=\"_r_a_10462372864\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" alt=\"Cash Flow \u0026#34;How was your little tete-a-tete with our Boss?\u0026#34;\" title=\"\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003csub\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere, we have a nepo-baby who was hired solely because of a personal connection to the CEO of a company. To make matters worse, this coworker didn\u0026#39;t just stop there. She also tried to impress the CEO by pretending that a report entirely written by another employee was her work. When she was caught in the act not even the CEO could defend her actions.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e02\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462358272/h4787E2DF/young-woman-who-only-got-her-job-especially-made-her-because-her-dad-golfing-buddies-with-our-ceo\" id=\"_r_a_10462358272\" width=\"800\" height=\"307\" alt=\"This was a young woman who only got her job (especially made for her) because her dad was golfing buddies with our CEO.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e03\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462358784/h57631B14/regularly-blamed-her-team-her-numerous-mistakes-and-took-all-credit-their-hard-work-lets-call-her-b\" id=\"_r_a_10462358784\" width=\"800\" height=\"308\" alt=\"She regularly blamed her team for her numerous mistakes, and took all the credit for their hard work. Let\u0026#39;s call her B☐\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e04\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462359296/h50A1C417/paper-reports-not-attachments-so-normally-printed-them-out-and-distributed-them-personally-staff\" id=\"_r_a_10462359296\" width=\"800\" height=\"703\" alt=\"I used to do trade shows and after the fall season would be back in the office and create a comprehensive report on the results of the shows, normally 15+ pages. The Veeps always wanted paper reports, not attachments, so I normally printed them out and distributed them personally to the staff.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e05\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462362112/hDD89CD23/corridor-then-watched-sheer-amazement-as-she-marched-straight-into-ceos-office-and-said-kid-not\" id=\"_r_a_10462362112\" width=\"800\" height=\"350\" alt=\"I handed B her copy as we B[ passed in the corridor, then watched in sheer amazement as she marched straight into the CEO\u0026#39;s office and said, I kid you not;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e06\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462358528/hA6C0F3D2/just-put-this-together-stunning-report-all-about-trade-shows-and-she-wasnt-even-same-department\" id=\"_r_a_10462358528\" width=\"800\" height=\"360\" alt=\"\u0026#34;Here Boss, I just put this together for you\u0026#34;. Stunning, the report was all about trade shows, and she wasn\u0026#39;t even in the same department!\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e07\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462373120/h20E5DB9B/planner-sales-comparison-quantity-company-company-company-c-5-32-25-34-30-no-27-2014-2015-2016-2017\" id=\"_r_a_10462373120\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" alt=\"5988 % MC MR M-M+ MU 27 S/AC 8 2 00 63 Comparison of Competitors UNIT SALES TRENDS Company A 2013 2014 505.155 $48485 Company B $363.236 Company C 1404.078 $585.842 2015 2016 2017 06.550 7073 5626.348 06372 $506.3.30 505.348 505.355 $747,459 28214 $900,000 $700,000 $600,000 $500,000 $400,000 $300,000 $200,000 $100,000 2013 2914 3015 2016 2017 UDGET PLANNER SALES COMPARISON QUANTITY Company A Company \u0026#34; 九 Company C • 5 32 25 34 \u0026#34; 30 NO 27 2014 2015 2016 2017\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003csub\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e08\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462359040/h8F3847DB/errors-let-have-back-and-get-revised-one-all-while-staring-at-ceo-with-slightly-raised-eyebrow\" id=\"_r_a_10462359040\" width=\"800\" height=\"582\" alt=\"Cue the revenge, I marched in there right after her, and said \u0026#34;Oh, B[ I just realized that my report has some numerical errors, let me have it back and I\u0026#39;ll get you a revised one\u0026#34;, all the while staring at the CEO with a slightly raised eyebrow.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e09\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462359552/h127A1355/as-left-heard-most-wonderful-words-ceo-aiku-would-please-close-door-as-leave\" id=\"_r_a_10462359552\" width=\"800\" height=\"321\" alt=\"As I left, I heard the most wonderful words from the CEO: \u0026#34;Aiku, would you please close the door as you leave?\u0026#34;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462360064/hAC280DC5/five-minutes-later-looking-like-ripe-tomato-couldnt-resist-asking-little-tete-tete-with-our-boss\" id=\"_r_a_10462360064\" width=\"800\" height=\"374\" alt=\"]came out about five minutes later looking like a ripe tomato. I couldn\u0026#39;t resist asking \u0026#34;How was your little tete-a-tete with our Boss?\u0026#34;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSeveral members of the online community congratulated the employee for thinking on their feet and standing up for themselves in front of the intimidating presence of their CEO. Keep scrolling below to see what they had to say about this!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462359808/h44A0C002/concerning-allegations-my-dad-asked-why-this-guys-variables-were-named-after-people-our-family-aka\" id=\"_r_a_10462359808\" width=\"728\" height=\"954\" alt=\"Disorderly_Chaos ⚫ My dad\u0026#39;s coworker tried to steal his programming code and take credit. At the meeting concerning the allegations... my dad asked why this guys variables were named after people in our family. AKA\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462360576/hD546E406/find-product-intriker-99-intpicard-1010\" id=\"_r_a_10462360576\" width=\"634\" height=\"432\" alt=\"Find Product [INT]$Riker = 9*9 [INT]$Picard = 10*10\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462360320/h8E45215A/chainsawarmlaserbear-s-up-but-would-hate-working-with-dad-lol-variable-names-help-understand-code\" id=\"_r_a_10462360320\" width=\"694\" height=\"678\" alt=\"ChainsawArmLaserBear. That\u0026#39;s up, but I would hate working with your dad lol Variable names help understand the code\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462360832/hCB148762/cabird78-and-kids-is-professionally-take-down-credit-stealing-coworker\" id=\"_r_a_10462360832\" width=\"746\" height=\"456\" alt=\"cabird78 And that, kids, is how you professionally take down a credit-stealing coworker.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462361088/h4F0C6FEC/took-all-credit-their-hard-work-lets-call-her-dont-even-need-read-rest-know-this-is-gonna-be-good\" id=\"_r_a_10462361088\" width=\"722\" height=\"830\" alt=\"DhibeCakes55. She regularly blamed her team for her numerous mistakes, and took all the credit for their hard work. Let\u0026#39;s call her I don\u0026#39;t even need to read the rest to know this .. is gonna be good...\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462361344/hE65E5201/had-gathered-while-working-with-team-this-involved-months-some-very-involved-measurements-over-long\" id=\"_r_a_10462361344\" width=\"622\" height=\"694\" alt=\"deadeyeAZ. I went to a meeting about some very detailed data I had gathered while working with a \u0026#34;team\u0026#34;. This involved months of some very involved measurements over long\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e17\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462361856/h975D75B6/parameters-lo-and-behold-all-my-work-presented-with-dont-know-who-did-this-but-this-is-great\" id=\"_r_a_10462361856\" width=\"656\" height=\"502\" alt=\"periods of time being correlated to specific testing parameters. Lo and behold all of my work was presented with \u0026#34;we don\u0026#39;t know who did this but this is great!\u0026#34; I\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e18\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10462361600/h2164E968/not-given-any-credit-my-revenge-years-later-he-got-walked-out-after-three-decades-working-company\" id=\"_r_a_10462361600\" width=\"726\" height=\"720\" alt=\"stood up and said \u0026#34;Well I do, it was me\u0026#34; and looked at the \u0026#34;team lead\u0026#34; who had not given me any credit for it. My revenge was years later when he got walked out after three decades of working for that company.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n            \u003cp\u003eStay up to date by following us on \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FailBlog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                \u003ch2\u003eTags\u003c/h2\u003e\n        \n\n            \n\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll down for the next article\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                \n\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003ch2\u003eAlso From FAIL Blog\u003c/h2\u003e\n        \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \n\n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
